CR Business Unit Management Plan Instance Record	CR Business Unit Management Plan Instance Record	Business Unit Management Plan Instance Record	##			Handles the oversight and management of the business unit activity	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Management Plan Period			The time period addressed by the management plan (typically this will include setting the default daily operating goals and arrangements for the business unit that is periodically updated)	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Usage Policies And Guidelines 			The policies and guidelines for business unit employees and service users	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Performance Goals			The target and actual business unit performance goals that are tracked by business unit management	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Operating Schedule 			The target and actual business unit operating schedule - recording planned and actual business activity 	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Operating Organization 			The assigned roles and responsibilities and associated work/delivery responsibilities for the staff making up the business unit	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Resource Plan			Details the number and skill profile of the business unit staff (target and actual)	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
			Business Unit Training Plan			Details of staff training and certification as appropriate	IO	IO		IO	O				IO			
BQ Performance Instance Record	BQ Performance Instance Record	Performance Instance Record	##			Monitor business unit activity, analyze performance and highlight divergence from the business unit management plan. This analysis can lead to re-assignments within the unit						IO	IO	O				
			Business Unit Resource Utilization			Record of the business unit employee target and actual utilization/productivity						IO	IO	O				
			Business Unit Output/Work Projections			Estimated projected business unit product/service delivery and work volume targets as appropriate for the type of unit						IO	IO	O				
			Business Unit Performance Statistics	##		Tracked business unit activity and performance statistics used to manage the business unit						IO	IO	O				
				Business Unit Performance Statistic Type		The type of activity that is tracked and analyzed (e.g. delivery rate, utilization)						IO	IO	O				
				Business Unit Performance Statistic Value		The statistical analysis that can include historical and trended views of the activity						IO	IO	O				
				Business Unit Performance Statistic Interpretation		Narrative that might explain any divergence from expected performance/delivery						IO	IO	O				
				Business Unit Performance Statistic Recommendation		Proposed operational changes/recommendations arising from the performance tracking and analysis						IO	IO	O				
BQ Troubleshooting Instance Record	BQ Troubleshooting Instance Record	Troubleshooting Instance Record	##			Overseeing the resolution of major production issues and initiating procedural changes as needed to reduce exposure to repeating occurrences									IO	IO	IO	O
			Business Unit Production Issue Record			A record of any production issues arising during the session (see Advanced Voice Channel Operations for detailed content)									IO	IO	IO	O
			Business Unit Issue Analysis And Recommended Response			A record of the root cause analysis for recurring issues and suggested remedial action that can be internal to the unit or recommended to service providers and subscribers as appropriate									IO	IO	IO	O